{
  "texts": [
    "He was allergic to gabapentin, and his family history was noncontributory.",
    "Examination on July 1 showed that his visual acuities were 20/40 RE and 20/50 LE.",
    "He had a subtle left afferent pupillary defect.",
    "He identified 11/11 Ishihara plates RE and 10/11 LE.",
    "His examination demonstrated corneal verticillate, in both eyes, and his extraocular motility was normal."
  ]
}